column16: Ian Kinsler grounds into double play, third baseman Adrian Beltre to second baseman Bill Hall to first baseman Kevin Youkilis.    Michael Young out at 2nd.
Michael Young singles on a ground ball to center fielder Eric Patterson.
Elvis Andrus grounds out, second baseman Bill Hall to first baseman Kevin Youkilis.
Chris Davis grounds out to first baseman Kevin Youkilis.
Bengie Molina hits a grand slam (5) to center field.   Vladimir Guerrero scores.    Nelson Cruz scores.    David Murphy scores.
David Murphy walks.    Michael Young scores.    Vladimir Guerrero to 3rd.    Nelson Cruz to 2nd.
